name: Don't Be a Dummy
comments: A 30 second long song, recorded as a jingle to advertise Lee Cooper jeans on independent television in UK.  Its inclusion in the Tubeway Army - Dance reissue was not listed on the CD packaging - the hidden track appears at the end of the first disc.  It was also later included with full credits in the 1999 CD reissue of The Plan compilation.
